        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "SQA acceptance criteria — MRL 5",
        "description": "Solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R1) holds ISO 9001:2015 certification; version-controlled input decks stored in Git with tagged release; automated regression suite covering 12 canonical benchmark cases passes at each release; documented change-control process with independent code review for hemolysis UDF."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is ISO 9001-certified. All simulation input files are version-controlled under Git tag v3.2.1. An automated regression suite of 12 benchmark cases (lid-driven cavity, backward-facing step, rotating disk, Stokes flow, and 8 hemolysis surrogates) passes without deviation. The in-house hemolysis power-law UDF underwent independent peer review and unit testing prior to integration. SQA evidence satisfies Gradation 4 requirements for MRL 5."
    },
