        "description": "Normalised RMS error (NRMSE) for hemolysis index < 15% across all five operating points; velocity field NRMSE < 10%; pressure-rise error < 5%; systematic bias assessed via Bland–Altman analysis with limits of agreement reported."
      },
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index NRMSE: 9.4% across five points (max 13.1% at 3 L/min / 2500 RPM). Velocity field NRMSE: 7.2%. Pressure-rise error: 2.8%. Bland–Altman analysis shows no systematic bias (mean difference −0.002 NIH, 95% LoA ±0.031 NIH). All acceptance criteria satisfied; Gradation 4 achieved."
    },
