      },
      "rationale": "Validation experiments use the identical FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry (hub/shroud/blade profiles per FDA benchmark specification). All five COU operating points are covered. Blood analogue (40% glycerin–water) viscosity matches clinical blood within 3.8% at 37 °C. Reynolds similarity: Re_exp / Re_COU = 0.997. Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU at Gradation 4."
